bug.short_desc: NPE when expanding comments in the task editor

long_desc.thetext:
when opening bug 325795, I occasionally see the following NPE and the editor becomes blank after pressing the '+' on the comments part.
I'm bootstrapped off of Mylyn master.
To reproduce: # open bug 325795 in the task editor # press the '+' button on the comments section # observe that the editor goes blank and the NPE shows up in the error log
the only known workaround is to open the bug in the web browser
